import React from 'react'

	HeaderContent,
	HeaderTitle,
	PartyContainer,
	PartyContent,
	PartyLeftColumn,
	PartyRightColumn,
	PartyWrapper,
	PartyImage,
	PartyName,
	PartyTitle,
	PartyCopy,

import { PageWrapper } from 'components'
import { bridalParty } from 'config/images'

export const BridalParty = () => {
	return (

			<Header>

			<PartyContainer>

						</PartyWrapper>
						<PartyWrapper>

								Augustana brought Courtney and Becca together on day 0 of Augustana

						</PartyWrapper>
